rows.label: qst200421_msg0001
rows.name:
Well done, friends!
Thank you for saving Punin!

rows.label: qst200421_msg0002
rows.name:
Punin in your debt,
and will certainly repay...one day!

rows.label: qst200421_msg0003
rows.name:
...We only did what's right.
No reward is necessary.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0005
rows.name:
It like Vasara not even listen when we
talk about importance of teamwork.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0006
rows.name:
Tora and friends follow Vasara!
Punin keep up good work!

rows.label: qst200421_msg0008
rows.name: That was a job and a half, wasn't it?

rows.label: qst200421_msg0009
rows.name:
But we avenged Ellenora.
I bet she's happy about that.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0010
rows.name: It was sketchy, but we pulled through.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0011
rows.name:
And we got our revenge!
I'm sure Ellenora'd be pleased.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0012
rows.name: It took a while, but vengeance is ours.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0013
rows.name:
I imagine Ellenora is smiling...
wherever she is.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0014
rows.name:
A job well done, Vasara!
I gotta say, it wasn't easy...

rows.label: qst200421_msg0015
rows.name:
But justice is served!
That's what Ellenora would've wanted.

rows.label: qst200421_msg0017
rows.name:
So long as there are those in need of
judgment, I will continue to mete it out
with this sword.
